  x = runif(100, 1, 5)

  screen(1)
  hist(x, probability = T)
  screen(2)
  boxplot(x, horizontal = T)
  close.screen(all.screens = T)

  ff = function(n = 2){
    x = runif(100, 1, 5)
    for(i in 2: n){
      x = x + runif(100, 1, 5)
    }
    x
  }
  rn = ff(100000)
  hist(rn, probability = T)
  lines(density(rn))
